Kaneshiro2015
=============

Visual object ERP dataset from Kaneshiro et al 2015.

Dataset Overview
----------------
  Code: Kaneshiro2015
  Paradigm: p300
  DOI: 10.1371/journal.pone.0135697
  Subjects: 10
  Sessions per subject: 1
  Events: human_body=1, human_face=2, animal_body=3, animal_face=4, fruit_vegetable=5, inanimate_object=6
  Trial interval: [0, 0.496] s
  File format: MATLAB
  Data preprocessed: True

Acquisition
-----------
  Sampling rate: 62.5 Hz
  Number of channels: 124
  Channel types: eeg=124
  Montage: GSN-HydroCel-128
  Hardware: EGI Net Amps 300
  Reference: average
  Sensor type: HydroCel Geodesic Sensor Net
  Line frequency: 60.0 Hz

