Experimental Protocol
---------------------
  Paradigm: p300
  Number of classes: 6
  Class labels: human_body, human_face, animal_body, animal_face, fruit_vegetable, inanimate_object
  Trial duration: 0.496 s
  Study design: Visual object recognition; 72 images from 6 categories; 500 ms presentation, 750 ms ISI
  Feedback type: none
  Stimulus type: photograph
  Stimulus modalities: visual
  Primary modality: visual
  Mode: offline

